<span id="Description"></span>
==Описание==

The '''Std ViewHome''' command changes the camera in the active [[3D_view|3D view]] to the default camera orientation. And zooms and pans the camera so that all visible objects fit inside the view.

<span id="Usage"></span>
==Применение==

# There are several ways to invoke the command:
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|View → Standard views → [[Image:Std_ViewHome.svg|16px]] Home}} option from the menu.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Standard views → [[Image:Std_ViewHome.svg|16px]] Home}} option from the [[3D_view|3D view]] context menu.
#* Use the keyboard shortcut: {{KEY|Home}}.

<span id="Preferences"></span>
==Настройки==

See also: [[Preferences_Editor|Preferences Editor]].

*  The default camera orientation can be customized: {{MenuCommand|Edit → Preferences... → Display → Navigation → Default camera orientation}}.


